catch sunlight reflected off the road 
midnight sun from the university of waterlooontario 
canada looks like a flying saucer gliding down the highway and 
the university of texas reportedly spent more than 1 million on 
its 340pound dynamo made out of carbon graphite 
many of the entrants and officials were talking about the unique 
