miles away by the planned rural route wednesday the drivers hope 
the cars will run 205 miles from tallahassee to montgomery ala 
via georgia 
the race is sponsored by gm the us department of energy and 
the society of automotive engineers gm and the energy department 
provided each school with 7000 in seed money to start their 
projects last year 
