that he also saw barry use marijuana and opium on several occasions 
at one cookout said roberts there was use of cocaine and 
opium 
roberts said the proposed testimony was to show the 
defendants predisposition toward controlled substances to 
counter defense claims that barry was trapped into using cocaine on 
jan 18 when he was arrested 
mohammadi said that as part of his agreement with prosecutors to 
