<TEXT>
police hunted monday for 
members of the white liberation army which claimed responsibility 
for a bombing that injured 27 blacks and threatened to carry out 
more such attacks to preserve white rule 
meanwhile four more white rightwing activists were arrested in 
connection with an investigation of a series of recent bomb attacks 
against opponents of the apartheid system according to police and 
