proof that the government was yielding to the anc and the 
communists who play an influential role in the black nationalist 
groups leadership 
the government is recklessly busy intimidating rightwingers 
in order to impress its communist party allies so that they can go 
to the negotiation table as fast as possible he said 
he warned there would be greater actions of resistance and 
anger from whites if those arrested continue to be held without 
trial 
the african national congress had earlier criticized police for 
failing to solve any of the recent bombings but on monday the 
group said it appreciated the arrests 
walter sisulu the anc internal leader said the movement had 
demanded rightwing suspects be detained as anc suspects had been 
in the past 
sisulu said there was an essential difference between the 
bombings committed by the rightwing extremists and the armed 
struggle launched by the anc against the white minority government 
in 1961 
he said the ancs struggle was part of a human rights campaign 
on behalf of disenfranchised blacks while the whites already had 
the vote and extensive privileges 
they just have no reason to take up arms except to act as 
terrorists sisulu said 
most rightwing whites are afrikaners the dutchdescended 
settlers of south africa who account for 3 million of the 5 million 
whites 
the rightwing whites want to maintain the apartheid system of 
racial separation that denies political and economic rights to the 
30 million black majority 
