for other aliens the consequences have been tragic 
ms chengs husband yick tak cheung is charged with smuggling 
dozens of aliens in small rubber rafts across the rapids below 
niagara falls some of the rafts were equipped with cellular phones 
that the aliens or their couriers could use to arrange for 
drivers to meet them on the us shore 
but they apparently were not equipped with life jackets and four 
aliens drowned when a raft deflated and sank in the icechoked 
river in late december 1988 
that was particularly cruel and callous on the part of the 
smugglers ingham says we perceive many of these aliens as 
victims 
