<TEXT>
here are signs of alcoholism in older 
people 
gaps in memory 
confusion 
aggressive or abusive behavior 
depression 
falling repeatedly 
having frequent automobile accidents 
neglect of appearance and hygiene 
talking about or attempting suicide 
neglect of home bills and pets 
a flushed face 
trembling 
weight loss 
extreme fatigue 
incontinence 
withdrawal from social activities 
